<L>__{int san simeon. hallways following}
<A>__{welles roams the seemingly endless hallways of san simeon. in the half light they begin to resemble his own cinematic dream palace, xanadu. he hears the ghostly echo of a song, "where or when". he curiously follows the sound, taking in the fabulous castle everywhere around him. he passes by the door to the assembly room. inside, shafts of light illuminate portions of huge, uncompleted jigsaw puzzles.}
